title: Surfing Naked - Mason Ho #LIVEARNETTE
description: Mason Ho comes from a surf dynasty, but that doesn't keep him from having fun in and out of the water. In this #LIVEARNETTE episode, Mason talks about surfing in Australia and the origin behind his nickname, Naked Mase.
